  "title": "Freight Sales Executive – Indoor Sales (Class 3 License Required)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Handle sales inquiries, prepare quotes, and present proposals to clients.</li>\n  <li>Maintain clear and effective communication with internal teams and external stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Create and implement sales strategies and marketing initiatives to drive growth.</li>\n  <li>Deliver exceptional customer service to build lasting client relationships and ensure satisfaction.</li>\n  <li>Conduct proactive outreach, including cold calls, to expand sales opportunities and meet targets.</li>\n  <li>Compile and analyze monthly sales performance reports.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
